Our Exhibitors 2024

Here you can find our exhibitors of FRUIT LOGISTICA 2024.

Are you interested in more information and would like to network with the contact persons of the exhibiting companies in the run-up to the trade fair? Then go to FRUIT LOGISTICA Online and create your personal profile free of charge!

Don't miss any of the highlights

For an optimised view on your smartphone, please use the FRUIT LOGISTICA App. Download our App to your mobile phone. Here you have the mobile hall plan, all program points and your saved favorites at your fingertips at any time.

Download our exhibitor list

You have the opportunity to download our exhibitor list as a up to date PDF. To do this, click on the tab "Exhibitors" below the search bar and then on the printer icon on the right below the alphabet bar.

Alternatively, you can download an Excel list (XLSX,120.4kB) (last status: 01.02.2024). The excel list is a interim status without any claim to completeness. Please always use FRUIT LOGISTICA Online or our exhibitor search via the website.
